Node "Seville_1_1d_3c"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I have to spell it out for you? Yes, he's dead, man. As in, we had to bury his ass under six feet of wasteland."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who's Rico?" linkto "Seville_1_1d_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What did you mean when you said he, 'ODed'?" linkto "Seville_1_1d_3b"  notes ""
