Node "Seville_1_2c_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[He turns to the rest of the group with him.] We know the Vultures, fellas? [There are theatrical murmurings from the group and someone laughs. The man turns back to you, wild-eyed.] We don't know any Vultures, mister."
 NPCFemaleText "[He turns to the rest of the group with him.] We know the Vultures, fellas? [There are theatrical murmurings from the group and someone laughs. The man turns back to you, wild-eyed.] We don't know any Vultures, lady."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you suggest where I should look for them?" linkto "Seville_1_2c_4a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're Seville, aren't you?" linkto "Seville_1_2c_4b" conditions { CHECK_STAT intelligence >= 6 link_next AND, CHECK_STAT perception >= 6 link_next NONE } notes "Note intelligence and perception checks."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're not Douglas' brother, then?" linkto "Seville_1_2c_4c_1"  notes "This option only appears if the PC has spoken to Douglas and know's that he's Seville's younger brother."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's a shame, because I need to warn them that Saman is hiring people to kill them." linkto "Seville_1_2c_4d"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go, goodbye." linkto "Seville_1_d_1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Seville_1_2c_4a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[He suppresses a chuckle.] No idea. Hey, I'll say you're looking for them if I ever meet them. [There's yet more laughter from the group.]\n"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks, I guess. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
