notes ""
{
NPCText "Big chief Alex doesn't like people having fun in Sandover. Apparently, because everyone's so ill in the caves, no-one's allowed to smile. We like to party, so, what the hell? We did."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Saman threw you out for partying?" linkto "Seville_3_2b_2b_2"  notes ""
